{"tid":1611374,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"尋日屯門大會堂嘅波牛全部入嚟","createTime":"2019-10-02T02:49:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T08:50:08.000Z","uid":88323,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9a734b254c03e82925c04f9e3578432fcd5f9ea5","tid":1611374,"uid":88323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:49:09.000Z","msg":"尋日我唔舒服食左藥 晏晝訓左<br />\n發夢個陣係屯門大會堂跟隊踢波<br />\n有幾樣嘢想講<br />\n<br />\n1. <br />\n一定要衡量情況（例如雙方人數、對方裝備） <br />\n只要你唔係弱智 我都幾肯定你有能力分辨邊邊優勢大啲<br />\n只要有明顯優勢 唔好諗咁多 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一個字：衝！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n2.<br />\n幾時衝都又係一個問題<br />\n尋日打左大概兩三波 我發現只要有少量手足肯衝<br />\n其他人都會勇武起來 <br />\n所以唔好怕做第一個（雖然我知好難）<br />\n做唔到第一個都好 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">都唔好賣甩衝左嘅手足</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n3.<br />\nTK<br />\n我尋日受嘅傷 除左中左啲椒之外<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我懷疑全部都係TK造成</strong></span><br />\n明白開拖個陣情況混亂 我無怪任何人<br />\n不過進攻個陣都要睇住身邊嘅人<br />\n<br />\n4.<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔敢打就唔好企最前</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">企得第一排就同我搏命打</span></strong><br />\n最後一波個陣<br />\n我本身係最前 點知望下有無玩具可以執個陣<br />\n已經俾人迫走左 去到第二三排 <br />\n個陣啲狗已經俾人迫左埋牆 <br />\n亦都好似有手足俾人撳左係地下<br />\n我不停叫「圍佢老母！」想救人<br />\n不過前面嘅人唔肯向前<br />\n<br />\n尋日嘅情況都有手足被捕 我覺得講唔過<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> 記得 相比打狗 救人重要好多</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n個夢好怪 <br />\n明明係踢緊波 點知變左打狗 又有隊友俾人拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人壓力太大"},{"pid":"16e60fb957cb0bbfcf6f1b1e44dae65dd8d04ec7","tid":1611374,"uid":15740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:49:25.000Z","msg":"Ok, push."},{"pid":"aaf13df9ba58a16441d57c726f7a57838a9ae264","tid":1611374,"uid":88323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16e60fb957cb0bbfcf6f1b1e44dae65dd8d04ec7","tid":1611374,"uid":15740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:49:25.000Z","msg":"Ok, push."},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:50:11.000Z","msg":"咁撚快 有無見架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a400f51991592e680a987d5958ccc42a11962213","tid":1611374,"uid":2526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:51:45.000Z","msg":"辛苦晒<br />\n我真係睇完架"},{"pid":"74922b762838551faf013a27f9142bcd54a171c7","tid":1611374,"uid":283622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aaf13df9ba58a16441d57c726f7a57838a9ae264","tid":1611374,"uid":88323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16e60fb957cb0bbfcf6f1b1e44dae65dd8d04ec7","tid":1611374,"uid":15740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:49:25.000Z","msg":"Ok, push."},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:50:11.000Z","msg":"咁撚快 有無見架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:52:05.000Z","msg":"有無睇呀下話?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nanyway, push.<br />\n不單只屯門, <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">ANYWHERE, ANYTIME, <br />\nNO MATTER POPO OR BLUE RIBBON</span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"950d8f75698833cb5952789ff6aa6b4634aac1a2","tid":1611374,"uid":69334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:53:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2f9f6b962b2df0b0e04b34dd40fdebcd0bd8dbb2","tid":1611374,"uid":88323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74922b762838551faf013a27f9142bcd54a171c7","tid":1611374,"uid":283622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aaf13df9ba58a16441d57c726f7a57838a9ae264","tid":1611374,"uid":88323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16e60fb957cb0bbfcf6f1b1e44dae65dd8d04ec7","tid":1611374,"uid":15740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:49:25.000Z","msg":"Ok, push."},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:50:11.0